                        <interp inst="t18380402-name-1368" type="given" value="HENRY"></interp>HENRY MORSE</persName>
                  </hi>. I am a printer; I am on a visit to my father. On the 22nd of March about eight o'clock at night, I was in the Borough, near Red Lion-court—I felt a tug at my pocket, and turned round instantly—the prisoner was near me—I saw my handkerchief in his possession—he threw it down—I stooped to pick it up, and he ran off—he was taken in about five minutes—I am sure he is the same person.</p>
